  "claim_boundary": [
    "This contract qualifies an allocation-free parser and caller-buffer loader boundary over synthetic ET_DYN images.",
    "The file is not authenticated by this layer; a future signed-manifest gate must authenticate exact bytes before loading.",
    "No UEFI filesystem read, AllocatePages call, page-table update, final memory map, ExitBootServices call, transfer assembly, or PooleKernel execution is exercised.",
    "The four mapping ranges are a required post-relocation plan, not evidence that hardware page permissions were installed.",
    "The accepted subset is intentionally not a general ELF dynamic linker and does not establish ABI ratification or production readiness."
